wikipedia_page.main: Lucy Renshall (born 11 December 1995) is a British judoka. She competed in the women's 63 kg event at the 2020 Summer Olympics held in Tokyo, Japan.She is the 2021 Judo Grand Slam Antalya champion in the -63 kg class. She also won the gold medal in her event at the 2021 Judo Grand Slam Baku held in Baku, Azerbaijan. She repeated this at the 2021 Judo Grand Slam Abu Dhabi held in Abu Dhabi, United Arab Emirates.
